  SEO:
    -
      title: Unique title and description
      content:
        Each page must contain a unique title tag and a unique meta description tag. Those can contain an emoji too. Emoji may increase CTR of your website in a search results page.
      more:
        Sometimes people copy existing pages and forget to change title and description. It is not obvious and not easily trackable mistake but it can damage your SEO.
      author: aisora
    -
      title: Human friendly URLs
      content:
        Set descriptive URLs. A visitor should understand what they will get by visiting the page. Do not use too much words.
      author: aisora
    -
      title: Robots.txt
      content:
        Make sure robots.txt is created, added to the root of the site. It is not hiding public directories and pages.
      author: aisora
    -
      title: Sitemap.xml
      content:
        Create sitemap.xml and constantly update it. Submit sitemap.xml to the <a href="https://www.google.com/webmasters" target="_blank"> Google Webmaster console</a>.
      author: aisora
    -
      title: 0 broken links
      content:
        Make sure your landing page doesn't contain broken links.
      more:
        There is a free <a href="https://ahrefs.com/broken-link-checker" target="_blank">tool</a> for that.
      author: aisora
