        <li>You can set different images for each website page.</li>
        <li>Facebook recommends the resolution of 1200x630. This size will work ~fine for other social networks but you can specify an exclusive image for Twitter.</li>
        </ul>
         Learn more on <a href="https://ogp.me/" target="_blank">the official website/a> or on this blog post <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/open-graph-meta-tags/" target="_blank">this blog post/a>.
